Package: power4peaks
Type: Package
Title: An R-package for power and sample size calculations for genpeaks data
Version: 0.1.0
Author: Sebastian Gregoricchio
Maintainer: Sebastian Gregoricchio <s.gregoricchio@nki.nl>
